SUMMARY:Deadline: Slamdance Film Festival 2027: DIG (Digital\, Interactive 
 and Gaming)
DESCRIPTION:Slamdance's DIG (Digital\, Interactive and Gaming) showcase pre
 sents work at the edges of cinema and interactivity: interactive documenta
 ries\, VR/AR\, experiential installations\, and experimental games\, a str
 ong fit for interactive AI and data-driven work. Film categories run on si
 milar deadline tiers. DIG deadlines: regular 10 August 2026 (USD 60)\, lat
 e 14 September 2026 (USD 70)\, extended 6 October 2026 (USD 90).\n\nOrgani
 sation: Slamdance\nLocation: Los Angeles\, California\, United States (fes
 tival 18-24 February 2027). Open to international entries.\nAward: Festiva
 l exhibition at Slamdance in Los Angeles. DIG welcomes interactive documen
 taries\, VR/AR\, experiential installations\, and genre-bending games. Ent
 ry fees: USD 60 regular\, USD 70 late\, USD 90 extended/final.\nDuration: 
 Festival 18-24 February 2027.\n\nMore: https://slamdance.com/festival-subm
 it/?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
URL:https://slamdance.com/festival-submit/?utm_source=artificialnouveaugran
 tdesk&utm_medium=referral
LOCATION:Los Angeles\, California\, United States (festival 18-24 February 
 2027). Open to international entries.
